OL,3,CPolice involved in car crash that
OL,4,Ckilled pedestrian 'acted appropriately'
OL,6,FPolice officers who were in a car that
OL,7,Fhit a father-of-two while responding
OL,8,Fto an emergency call "acted
OL,9,Fappropriately", a watchdog has found.
OL,11,FRoger Bagnall, 40, died after trying
OL,12,Fto cross Yardley Road in Acocks Green,
OL,13,FBirmingham, on the evening of 19 March
OL,14,Flast year. He was struck by a West
OL,15,FMidlands Police car, which had its
OL,16,Femergency lights and sirens on.
