OL,3,CPolice involved in car crash that
OL,4,Ckilled pedestrian 'acted appropriately'
OL,6,FCCTV footage showed Mr Bagnall stepped
OL,7,Finto the road as the police car
OL,8,Fapproached at a speed of 55-61mph, the
OL,9,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,10,F(IOPC) said.
OL,12,FThe officer driving the car slowed to
OL,13,F25-35mph and appeared to try to steer
OL,14,Faround Mr Bagnall, the IOPC said. But
OL,15,Fthe father ran into the path of the
OL,16,Fvehicle, seemingly trying to run
OL,17,Facross the road.
OL,19,FAn inquest into his death concluded on
OL,20,FFriday that he died due to a road
OL,21,Ftraffic collision, the IOPC said.
