OL,3,CPolice involved in car crash that
OL,4,Ckilled pedestrian 'acted appropriately'
OL,6,FThe police car was double crewed and
OL,7,Fwas responding to reports that a man
OL,8,Fhad been seen nearby carrying knives.
OL,10,FIOPC director Derrick Campbell said:
OL,11,F"Our sympathies are with Mr Bagnall's
OL,12,Ffamily and friends, and to all those
OL,13,Faffected by his death and the tragic
OL,14,Fnature of it.
OL,16,F"In line with our role we
OL,17,Findependently looked at the
OL,18,Fcircumstances of the collision, along
OL,19,Fwith the actions and decisions of the
OL,20,Fofficers involved.
