OL,6,FMr Bagnall was described by his
OL,7,F"devastated" family as a "beloved
OL,8,Fpartner, dad, brother and son" in a
OL,9,Ftribute.
OL,11,FHis relatives had said: "Roger had the
OL,12,Fbiggest heart and loved to make
OL,13,Feveryone smile with his humour and
OL,14,Fwit. We loved him very much and will
OL,15,Fmiss him dearly, but we take comfort
OL,16,Fin the fact his spirit will live on
OL,17,Fthrough his children."
